HEADWORD: Earthstar
<hw>Earth"star`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>A curious fungus of the genus <gen>Geaster</gen>, in which the
outer coating splits into the shape of a star, and the inner one forms a
ball containing the dustlike spores.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>earth tones</ent>⟦br⟧
